ion of vice president business development in september  from  until he joined the company mr hart worked as an associate with hogan  hartson llp now hogan lovells us llp a leading international law firm where his practice focused on securities corporate governance and mergers and acquisition  read more danny hart our vice president business development joined the company in january  as the companys corporate counsel since joining the company mr hart was promoted to associate corporate counsel and assistant secretary in april  to deputy general counsel and assistant secretary in january  and then to his current position of vice president business development in september  from  until he joined the company mr hart worked as an associate with hogan  hartson llp now hogan lovells us llp a leading international law firm where his practice focused on securities corporate governance and mergers and acquisitions before joining hogan  hartson mr hart began his legal career at skadden arps slate meagher  flom llp a leading international law firm where he focused on corporate restructurings mr hart received a ba from the university of washington in seattle and a jd from vanderbilt university law school source pdl biopharma inc on    sign up for equilar atlas and view danny j hart jrs full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like danny j hart jr more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in danny j hart jrs network and community follow changes in danny j hart jrs employment and moneyinmotion connect with danny j hart jr through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example danny j hart jr danny j hart jrs connections  sign up now to view danny j hart jrs  connections » paul r edick board member newlink genetics corporation frederick frank board member landec corporation peter s garcia vice president and chief financial officer p